 alternative therapies and warfarin." Am J Health Syst Pharm 57 (2000): 1221-7; quiz 1228-30[4] Srivstava KC, Malhotra N "Acetyl eugenol, a component of oil of cloves (Syzygium aromaticum L.) inhibits aggregation and alters arachidonic acid metabolism in human blood platelets." Prostaglandins Leukot Essent Fatty Acids 42 (1991): 73-81', 1767365209);
